Oracle Corporation Buys Taleo Corporation
Thursday, 9 Feb 2012 08:01am EST
Oracle Corporation announced that it has entered into an agreement to acquire Taleo Corporation, a provider of cloud-based talent management for $46.00 per share or approximately $1.9 billion, net of Taleo's cash and debt. The Board of Directors of Taleo has unanimously approved the transaction. The transaction is expected to close mid-year 2012.Â 
